<p>Via <a href="https://twitter.com/climagic">climagic</a>'s <a href="https://twitter.com/climagic/status/692821765110767616?refsrc=email&amp;s=11">make slideshow from *.jpg</a>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-{.bash">for p in *.jpg; do
    ffmpeg -loop_input -f image2 -i $p -t 3 -r 4 -s 1080x720 -f avi - &gt;&gt; slides.avi;
done
</code></pre>
